This Project is for Hibernate

A)Hibernate

a)Maven

1)Project Management Tool.
2)To manage dependencies.
3)Hibernate core dependency.

b)Entity(Class)

1)Class is like Table and properties are columns.
2)Annotations to declare, @Entity, @Id(Primary key), @Table.

c)Main Code

1)Hibernate helps in simply using Objects to save data in SQL.
2)Make a Session using SessionFactory and Session Classes.
3)To fulfill ACID properties use Transaction Class and commit transaction.
4)Use Configuration Class to add you Entity Class.

d)Caching

1)Level 1 Caching - Automatic caching for same query in same session.
2)Level 2 Caching - Add dependency, make configuration for enabling caching for same query in different sessions.

e)HQL

1)Hibernate Query Language.
2)Similar to SQL.
3)Use Session to create query.
4)query.list() and query.uniqueResult() to get data.


f)JPA

1)Java Persistence API.

